	   <tr><td colspan=2>I just got lvl 41 and decided to go see what velious had to offer. I've been there and Giants con threateningly, I haven't seen any dragons or dwarfs to con yet. My question is for you who have decided which sid to align with. I'm looking for some advice on which side to take and some good reasons why. I've looked at the quest armor and the quest items the giants give seem to have slightly better stats than skyshrine or dwarves. I would appreciate any suggestions or comments on which faction would be better to ally with.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
