	   <tr><td colspan=2>About level 8-10 you can hunt rabid wolves and grizzlies in Qeynos Hills.&nbsp;&nbsp;When you kill them they drop a diseased pelt.  Take that pelt to the woman dressed in Leather Armor in the UFO in Qeynos--I think it is the Temple of Life.  Give her one at a time, you get great exp, a random item and she cures your disease.  If you have a group it will be much easier to kill these off at this level--and you will get more pelts.  Beware though of Holly--she roams the lands and protects all wolves and bears--and will kill on you sight in seconds.  Happy Hunting!<br>&nbsp;<br>Kolianu Fyrestorm, Retired member of Vazaelle.</td></tr>
